703815f-a.title: Brooklyn: Cornelia Street - Wilson Avenue
703815f-a.text:
(1)
Cornelia Street, at the N.E. corner of Wilson Ave., showing the
low frame annex building of P.S. No. 106, which also housed the Citizen's
Democratic Club. It was rased in June 1928.
January 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
(2)
The same, showing P.S. No. 106 at the N.W. corner.
January 1925.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
